{
  "texts": [
    "We used the latest editions of authoritative medical texts like the Merck Manual Professional Edition and the most current case studies relevant to the scenario, sourced via Bing AI search.",
    "An example of such a correction might be: 'This doesn't seem quite right.",
    "Here is the latest from Merck on diagnosing Obsessive-Compulsive Personality Disorder...', followed by detailed criteria.",
    "These web-informed responses were also re-assessed for accuracy by the expert, employing the same evaluation criteria as used for the initial self-correction process.",
    "[29][30][31][32][33][34][35][36] Re-evaluation of accuracy for self-corrected, revised responses from LLM-chatbots Detailed qualitative analysis of poorly-rated LLMchatbot responsesTo further elucidate the potential limitations and risks of relying solely on LLM-Chatbot responses for information on adolescent growth and development, we undertook a more detailed analysis."
  ]
}